raw_text = "~ start
##8:27pm
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Nina: You've gotta be the dumbest cub in that whole frat
Nina: You actually named my ass for your weird date
Nina: The one bitch in the house who can't stand the sight of you
- I did
	Player: I did
- 😝
	Player: 😝
Nina: You actually have a death wish huh
Nina: You seriously don't know who you're fucking with
Nina: Even told Jess hell no
Nina: And she STILL hit me with that \"rules are rules\" crap 🙄
Nina: So now I'm stuck blowing my fucking Saturday on you
Player: So is that a no?
Nina: Ha. Wish it was, bucko
Nina: And you didn't even hesitate
Nina: You just blurted it out like a damn puppy 🖕
Nina: Congrats. You bought yourself a whole Saturday of me
Nina: img: nina/19
Nina: You'll pay the price
- Feeling shy? [#blackheart]
	set Story.black_heart += 1
	Player: Feeling shy?
	Nina: HAH, not in your wildest dreams punk
	Nina: img: nina/20
	Nina: I don't give a fuck
	Nina: Think of it as pity since you'll never get your grimy little fingers on anything
- That was rude
	Player: That was rude
	Nina: Well get used to it punk
Nina: Besides
Nina: Let's not pretend I don't know exactly who you are
Nina: You think Maple's your little house pet
Nina: The one with a girlfriend, sniffing around MY skirt?
Nina: Does she even know how much of a sleazebag you are?
- I'm just following the rules
	Player: I'm just following the rules
	Player: Same as you
	Nina: Don't fucking use that as your shield
- It's not like that
	Player: It's not like that
	Nina: It's never \"like that\"
	Nina: You'll say that right up until the end and it'll never work
Nina: I know your type
Nina: Seriously remind me of someone I knew
Nina: But you're all the fucking same
Player: I guess you have your mind made up about me
Nina: Pfft
Nina: You know what's annoying about you?
Player: ?
Nina: Most of the new cubs freeze up and drool when I so much as look at them
Nina: You talk back like you're worth shit
Nina: You really stand out in the worst way possible
Nina: It's less boring but don't let it go to your head
Player: Wouldn't dream of it
Nina: Good
Player: Strong feelings but we should probably plan our date
Nina: Fuck it. Saturday
Nina: We do this MY way or we don't do it at all
Nina: I pick the place, I pick the time, you show up and you shut up
Player: And if I don't?
Nina: Then you waste a free night AND piss me off
Nina: Your call, genius
- Fine, your rules
	Player: Fine. Your rules
	Nina: So you CAN learn
- I think I can handle you [#blackheart]
	set Story.black_heart += 1
	Player: I think I can handle you
	Nina: HAH
	Nina: Oh that's adorable
	Nina: You have no idea what you just signed up for
Nina: I'll send you the details later
Nina: Do yourself a favor
Nina: Keep an eye on that girl you call yours this week heh
Player: You're just trying to get in my head
Nina: Trying?
Nina: I'm already in there, loser 🖕
Player: Well, good night!
Nina: img: nina/21
Nina: Ugh just. fuck. off.
=> END"
